## CLI vs LibreChat Reality

### ‚ùå CLI Tool Calling (What We Just Tested)

**Result:** Models don't reliably call tools via raw API
- Qwen3-32B: Responds with internal knowledge
- DeepSeek-V3: Says "I can't search the web"

**Why:** Direct API access doesn't have LibreChat's MCP integration layer

### ‚úÖ LibreChat MCP (Your Actual Setup)

**Result:** Tools work properly through LibreChat UI
- LibreChat handles tool orchestration
- MCP servers execute tools
- Models receive tool results
- Response includes real-time data

**Why:** LibreChat has special MCP integration layer

